🤝 Contributing # 👻 IdleGhost

Feel free to fork this repo, submit PRs, or suggest improvements!

Simulate user activity to prevent idle detection by trackers like Hubstaff and Time Doctor.

## 🔧 Features
- Mouse movement, keystrokes, and scroll simulation
- Fun, sarcastic terminal messages
- Ctrl+C global detection to stop the app
- Auto-start, auto-minimize, background behavior

## 🚀 Getting Started

### 1. Clone the repo
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/IdleGhost.git
cd IdleGhost
pip install -r requirements.txt
python idleghost.py
pyinstaller --noconsole --onefile --icon=icon.ico idleghost.py








